1587
01:19:11,074 --> 01:19:12,734
- Thank you.
- Thanks.

1588
01:19:12,874 --> 01:19:14,303
Thank you.

1589
01:19:14,304 --> 01:19:16,274
- Thank you.
- Thank you. Bye.

1590
01:19:16,744 --> 01:19:17,943
- Thanks.
- Thank you.

1591
01:19:17,944 --> 01:19:19,014
